title: Switching Service Providers for e-Residency Companies in Estonia
---

It is very easy to switch service providers if they accept already registed companies. Some providers can only accept clients who would register the company with their service. 

The two service providers I used/been using provide the switching service.

There is a state fee (€25) for changing legal address (a must step for switching service provider). 

The new and old providers will handle the neceesary documents for you.

Fun fact: I decided to switch back to xolo two weeks ago and companio announced just two days ago that they will charge for the annual report preparation. 

